<h2>simplevis: Simple Visualisation with 'ggplot2' and 'leaflet' Wrappers</h2>
<p>Support effortless high quality 'ggplot2' and 'leaflet' visualisations for reports or interactive 'shiny' apps through wrapping functions.</p>
